data.description: ***PRICE IMPROVEMENT BY $29,000***Welcome to your dream coastal retreat! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers the  perfect blend of comfort and luxury in a tranquil setting. Nestled on a double lot, this property boasts  an expansive circular driveway and a concrete parking pad, providing ample space for your boat,  RV, and golf cart – a true haven for outdoor enthusiasts.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that fills every corner of this  charming residence. The open concept living space seamlessly connects the interior with the  outdoor entertainment area, creating a perfect setting for hosting friends and family.  The heart of this home is the 18x30-foot pool, surrounded by a generous patio area and covered  seating spaces, ideal for relaxation and enjoying the Florida sun. An outdoor bar completes this  oasis, making it the ultimate spot for entertaining.  One of the most enchanting features of this property is its backyard, which backs up to a coastal  marsh wildlife and bird sanctuary along the Gulf of Mexico. You'll relish the serene and peaceful  ambiance as you immerse yourself in the beauty of nature.  This home has been thoughtfully designed and meticulously maintained, with a host of recent  updates. The roof is only 8 years old, and the A/C system has been replaced approximately 8 years  ago. The 15,000-gallon pool has been recently resurfaced, and the pool deck has been refurbished  for your enjoyment. There's even a convenient outdoor shower for a quick rinse after a dip in the  pool.  Inside, you'll find a well-appointed kitchen with plenty of cabinets, granite countertops, and all the  space you need for culinary adventures. Each bedroom features a walk-in closet, offering ample  storage space. The guest bathroom provides easy pool access, and the entire house is move-in  ready with fresh paint throughout.  This property is situated in the canal community of Sea Pines, offering access to the Gulf of Mexico  via the community association boat ramp. Best of all, there's no HOA to worry about! Sea Pines  Civic is a deed-restricted waterfront community that gives residents key fob access to a private boat  ramp, two parks, and a clubhouse for holiday gatherings and family events. It's a vibrant Florida  lifestyle community with shopping, waterfront restaurants, and outdoor water activities just a stone's  throw away.  For those seeking adventure, you're conveniently close to Weeki Wachee Springs and the Weeki  Wachee River for kayaking, as well as Hudson Beach and SunWest Water Adventure Park.  And here's the icing on the cake: this house stood strong during Hurricane Idalia and did not flood,  ensuring your peace of mind during Florida's storm season.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your new home – where everyday living  feels like a vacation. Come and experience the magic of coastal living at its finest!
